SELECT u.username AS user, COUNT(uf.feedback_id) AS total_feedback, AVG(uf.rating) AS avg_rating FROM users u LEFT JOIN user_feedback uf ON u.user_id = uf.user_id GROUP BY u.username HAVING avg_rating >= 4;
